{"tid":1848213,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"(我要全世界知道) 停發內地個人遊到港簽證根本就係廢","createTime":"2020-01-28T10:41:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-28T15:24:51.000Z","uid":168758,"like":560,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":149,"replies":[{"pid":"78f2bb07cad95b0eaaed0f4a53d4f4d1d87ab4f0","tid":1848213,"uid":168758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T10:41:48.000Z","msg":"因為2017年8月開始 辦理「團隊旅遊簽註」（L簽) 嘅旅客就可以直接通關 唔使再跟旅行團<br />\n<br />\n而且<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">自由行城市可以申請自由行簽注，而全國任何一個人都可以申請團簽</span></span><br />\n<br />\n即係<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">團簽 = 個人簽</span></span><br />\n<br />\n停咗個人簽 有春用!!!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係深圳過關 出邊有部自動簽註機整個團簽 2分鐘就搞掂 人人申請得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n政府無可能唔知!!!! <br />\n<br />\n補link (sor係紅01 但得佢有報道): <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/217765/內地改團隊旅遊-l簽-政策一年-變相自由行通全國-港府不知情\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F217765%2F%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E6%94%B9%E5%9C%98%E9%9A%8A%E6%97%85%E9%81%8A-l%E7%B0%BD-%E6%94%BF%E7%AD%96%E4%B8%80%E5%B9%B4-%E8%AE%8A%E7%9B%B8%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1%E8%A1%8C%E9%80%9A%E5%85%A8%E5%9C%8B-%E6%B8%AF%E5%BA%9C%E4%B8%8D%E7%9F%A5%E6%83%85&d=rcEdfnhTqGmqsB%2B6X%2FYCGZR%2B4kUINcy65scadR%2F1ewI%3D&h=ff15cb75\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/217765/內地改團隊旅遊-l簽-政策一年-變相自由行通全國-港府不知情</a>"},{"pid":"219bb7a9391ee74bdf12df76fef9e8f8d334ddbe","tid":1848213,"uid":168758,"like":73,"dislike":3,"score":70,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T10:42:29.000Z","msg":"做少少扮封咗 屌你林奠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4edde68f0d792aefe2f5d151824a12e3a1f5d81","tid":1848213,"